{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were telling me that things were getting pretty bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was only about 11 years old at the time, but I mean, I already, when I got these cards saying that, for instance, there were four families that they were telling me about-- the Eimers, who were distant cousins, the Ecklings, who were distant cousins, the Schwartzes and Hipshers-- they had left Austria and had-- those has come to the United States, for instance.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "How they got visas, I don't know, but I kept getting news about it was getting worse and worse in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, it wasn't getting better where we were, also.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Until June of 1940, when the Germans occupied Paris-- there was not more than a week or so before the Germans occupied Paris that the OSE took the kids and started sending them to other homes in-- outside of the Paris area.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Several homes were set up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was one home set up near Limoges, Chateau-- Chateau Montintin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Another one near Limoges, Chateau Masgelier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Another one near Vichy, which had already existed-- that was primarily for French kids-- in Chateau des Morelles.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At that time, I remember having a choice of going to either Chateau des Morelles, or Chateau Montintin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had a directrice, who was going-- who I liked, that nobody else seemed to like, but for some reason or other I liked her.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she initially said she was going to go to Chateau des Morelles near Vichy, so I said I want to go with her.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So she put me on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But then she changed her mind, and wound up-- or somebody changed their mind-- and she wound up near Chateau Montintin.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When I found that out, I asked her, I want to still go with her.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
